      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this beauty. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It drives like an absolute dream and is basically flawless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade Mazda RX-7 FD, featuring the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example boasts factory-spec compression and a pristine vacuum system, ensuring the complex sequential boost transition remains seamless. The front-midship chassis maintains its structural integrity, paired with an all-aluminum double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for uncompromising lateral grip. Every component, from the oil metering pump to the thermal management system, has been scrutinized to ensure peak performance. This is a rare, turn-key opportunity for the discerning collector seeking a mechanically flawless icon of the golden era of JDM performance.",
